oug Deeprose Doug Richardson Greg Staple John DeGelder Kurt Turcan Ron Armstrong SubjectFort Nelson Plant Redesign To All interested parties in the Fort Nelson Area We have a project underway to redesign the processing capacity of our Fort Nelson facility A key element of the project plan is to ensure stakeholders are informed of the benefits and impacts of the planned increase in throughput capacity and that a process of regular communicatio n and update is in place Please find enclosed for your information a projec t status report All the account managers are well aware of this exciting initiative and can answer any questions you may have which are not fully addressed in the briefing document Alternatively you may also contact me with any further questions or inquiries Customer Fact Sheet Final doc Gary C Weilinger Director Marketing Westcoast Energy Inc Pipeline Field Services Div The Dome Tower TD Square th Ave SW Calgary AB TP Z Fax Cell Customer Fact Sheet Final doc

ALLIANCE OUTAGE JUNE Lpst Forwarded by Liz PriorCALECT on AM Liz Prior PM To Dianne CT Desrae CT Laura E CT Chad CT Ryan CT Jeff CT cc Peggy CT Kevin CT Grant CT Subject ALLIANCE OUTAGE JUNE JUST A REMINDER THE ALLIANCE WINDFALL COMPRESSOR OUTAGE IS GOING AHEAD JUNE AND THE FOLLOWING PLANTS WILL NOT FLOW ONTO ALLIANCE DURING THIS TIME ABA WOLF SOUTH ABB EDSON AB EDSON AB KAYBOB AB W WHITECOURT AB TWO CREEKS AB KAYBOB AB KAYBOB SOUTH AB WASKAHIGAN AB KARR AB WAPITI AB WEMBLEY AB KNOPCIK THE FOLLOWING PLANTS WILL BE ABLE TO FLOW PARTIAL VOLUMES AB BIGSTONE ABA ELMWORTH ALLIANCE IS LETTING SHIPPERS PACK THEIR ACCOUNTS IN PREPARATION FOR THIS OUTAGE AND WITH AOS OFFERED THEY WILL ALLOW SHIPPERS TO SELL BASE FIRM TRANSPORT TO CHICAGO ON THOSE DAYS SO WE ARE GOING TO SEE THIS PIPE PACK PRIOR TO THE OUTAGE AND THEN DRAFT BACK ON THE TH AND TH ANY OTHER QUESTIONS GIVE ME A CALL THANKS LIZ

Coming to VisitHey guys Im coming to Houston October th th and I was hoping that we could do lunch or dinner or something Let me know if your going to be around and maybe we can hookup Thanks Liz Prior

RE Coming to VisitI will be in on Saturday evening so I could do lunch on Sunday Monday or Tuesday Pick a day and I will plan for it I know you are busy so I will let you pick Original Message From Tycholiz Barry Sent Tuesday September AM To Prior Liz Subject RE Coming to Visit I was in Denver when the attacks occured and then I drove from Denver to Houston hours to get home I was not in the office until thurs afternoon BT Original Message From Prior Liz Sent Tuesday September AM To Tycholiz Barry Subject RE Coming to Visit Hey that sounds great Were you on holidays last week or just really busy I was suprised I didnt hear from you earlier Cant wait to see Houston Liz Original Message From Tycholiz Barry Sent Tuesday September AM To Prior Liz Subject RE Coming to Visit I am sure I will be here Let me take you out for lunch BT Original Message From Prior Liz Sent Monday September PM To Tycholiz Barry Dietrich Dan Subject Coming to Visit Hey guys Im coming to Houston October th th and I was hoping that we could do lunch or dinner or something Let me know if your going to be around and maybe we can hookup Thanks Liz Prior
